description: If you are thinking it's about time to move away to Mars after going through the 2016 US election options, you can ask Alexa to give you some facts about life on Mars and what you can expect when you get there. There are so many positive aspects to this.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask life on mars to give me something about life on Mars
Alexa, ask life on mars for a mars fact
Alexa, tell life on mars to give me some Mars information
name: Life on Mars Facts
shortDescription: This skill provides interesting facts about life on the planet Mars.
